RALPH v. WARDEN, MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 1,

September Term, 1968.]

Decided September 19, 1968.

Before Hammond, C. J., and Marbury, McWilliams, Singley and Smith, JJ.

Per Curiam :

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Joseph M. Mathias in the court below.

Application denied.
